<body>

  <h1>Student Opportunity Hub</h1>
  <p>
    Student Opportunity Hub is a simple platform designed to help students find
    internships, scholarships, hackathons, and learning opportunities in one place.
  </p>

  <h2>Problem</h2>
  <p>
    Students often miss important opportunities because information is scattered
    across multiple websites and social media platforms.
  </p>

  <h2>Our Solution</h2>
  <p>
    This platform collects important student opportunities and displays them
    in a simple and easy-to-use format.
  </p>

  <h2>Features</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Internships and scholarships listing</li>
    <li>Hackathon and course information</li>
    <li>Category-based browsing</li>
    <li>Simple and clean interface</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Future Scope</h2>
  <p>
    In future, we plan to add personalized recommendations and notifications
    for upcoming deadlines.
  </p>

  <p><b>Prototype created for Hackathon Round 1</b></p>

</body>
</html>
